<% title "United States Hospital List" %>
<% description 'Listing of American Hospitals. Click to compare hospital costs in the US' %>
<% keywords "chargemaster rates, medicare rates, compare health costs, most expensive hospitals" %>

<h2>Hospitals Listing</h2>
<p class="lead">The <a href="http://www.cms.gov/" target="_blank">Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services</a> released billing data for the top 100 Diagnosis Related Groups (DRGs) in 2011 for more than 3000 U.S. Hospitals. View this data by searching for the Hospital's region and then selecting the hopsital name. You can also view <a href="/region/all/">all U.S. Hospitals in one list</a>.</p>

